Right now this may or may not compile. Please don't use this repo
for simulations the moment. I'm trying to build it in a more sane manner :)


For API reference to GEANT4 use: http://www-geant4.kek.jp/Reference/


Compiling

In a separate build directory type:

cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=ReleaseWithDebugInfo /path/to/source/code
make
